Utterance.UttText: Raquel Soares caetano, 62 under Dr Mills, came in with chest pain, tiredness, dizziness and depression.
She's got a history diabetes and she is obese.
She's a new admission and just came in 3 hours ago.
She complains of pain everytime she eats but it doesn't seem to be related to her digestion.
She is here for further investigations.
